2 Violin plots

vioplot package

vioplot::vioplot(pseudo)

vioplot(mtcars$mpg, mtcars$qsec)

with(mtcars, vioplot(mpg[cyl==4] , mpg[cyl==6], mpg[cyl==8],  col=rgb(0.1,0.4,0.7,0.7) , names=c("A","B","C") ))

plot(mtcars$mpg,mtcars$disp, xlim=c(0,50), ylim=c(0,500))
vioplot(mtcars$mpg, col="tomato", horizontal = TRUE, at=-2, add = TRUE, lty=2, rectCol = "gray")
vioplot(mtcars$disp, col = "cyan", horizontal = FALSE, add=TRUE)

vioplot(mpg ~ cyl, data = mtcars)

treatment=c(rep("A", 40) , rep("B", 40) , rep("C", 40) )
value=c( sample(2:5, 40 , replace=T) , sample(c(1:5,12:17), 40 , replace=T), sample(1:7, 40 , replace=T) )
data=data.frame(treatment,value)
 
# Draw the plot
with(data, vioplot( value[treatment=="A"] , value[treatment=="B"], value[treatment=="C"],  col=rgb(0.1,0.4,0.7,0.7) , names=c("A","B","C") ))
